{
  "chapter": 106,
  "chapter_summary": "寇仲与徐子陵在后山方亭谈心，寇仲倾诉对李秀宁的失恋之痛，徐子陵以调侃与关怀相伴。随后二人奉召见商秀洵，寇仲归还井中月宝刀，商秀洵对宝刀的古朴质感颇感兴趣，寇仲趁机吹嘘宝刀通灵。商秀洵命二人演练刀法，寇仲故作姿态逗得佳人开怀。大执事梁治急报四大寇先锋二千人逼近牧场西面，商秀洵冷静部署。寇徐二人推测四大寇真正目标是李秀宁，幕后主谋或为李密、王世充、薛举之一，遂决定分工：寇仲主内查内奸配合李秀宁，徐子陵主外对付四大寇。二人前往鲁妙子处求助，鲁妙子启动地下机关，展示毕生收藏——机关学、天文地理兵法等六部著作，以及面具、飞天神遁等精巧器物，叮嘱二人面具可易容今夜派上用场，巧器虽妙但不可倚仗妨碍武道修习，最后赠予面具与飞天神遁助二人应战。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "幸好我当时说赶着上茅厕，否则美人儿场主抓起我来顺口一问，我们就要跳往下面去了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凭我们的功夫，跳下去该不会跌死吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你为何不问我和李秀宁间刚才发生过甚么事呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你不是说过长生诀的武功令你变得愈来愈冷酷无情吗？又说可为争霸天下而不择手段，牺牲一切。既是如此，我还须向你恳求答案吗？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "陵少今次错了，事实上我的感觉是窝囊至极。因为我竟忍不住问她是否已嫁了给柴绍那混蛋。想想吧！陵少！假若她答我'仍未嫁人'，我可怎样向她交代呢？而明知此问只是作茧自缚，我仍要问她。你说这是甚么一回事哩！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那她怎样答你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "她说的是虽未正式嫁人，但已等若嫁了人差不多。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那即是说她爱的是柴绍了。这句话确很难捱，亦使我第一次感到你值得被同情。跟着你如何还招呢？情场上的招式，比战场上生死对决的招式更使人头痛，只不过伤害的是双方的心罢了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "于是我化悲愤为力量，告诉她我毫不介意，还感激她赐我失恋的痛心滋味；强忍着吻她的强烈冲动，冲出房门去，背着她时，我痛苦得整个人麻木了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那你有否躲在茅厕里痛哭流涕呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你不是在同情我可怜我吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "因为值得被同情的那人再不是你，而是李秀宁。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我确是过分了点，但当时真有种愈能伤害她，便愈是痛快的感觉。那是一种完全失控的情绪，使我自己心知肚明我仍是很看紧她。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "于是你就出尽混身解数，设法在这弹指般短暂的时间内，务要令她忘不了你。这对她是多么残忍无辜的事呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "杀了我吧！我现在痛苦得要命。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我说话太没技巧了！男女间事就是如此，根本没道理可言，谁的护体神功强一些，谁就少受点伤害。不过看来你的护体神功很难及格。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你还说没有技巧，现在我就只想痛哭一场。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你每趟失恋，都是拉着我来搞混，所以我才是真正的受害者。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "为甚么早有第一次失恋的经验，第二趟仍是这么难受！且更是厉害呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "有甚么稀奇，因你爱得她更深了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你这话不无道理，时间久了，水也可滴穿坚石，所以现在我的心该是百孔千洞，这叫心内滴泪大法，与鲁妙子的遁去的一异曲同工，因为李秀宁就是我那遁去的一。即使商秀洵比她胜上半筹，我心中仍只有她。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "米已成炊，再也休提。我们下一步该怎样下法才合弈剑之道呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "先设法找那荡妇出来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "若可逐间房去敲门就好啦。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "以你的绝世耳功，要偷听方圆百里内的一把荡声，该不会是甚么困难的事吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "真夸张，来吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_juan",
      "speaker_name": "小娟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "找着你们了！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "馥大姐",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "两位小师傅到了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "宝刀到了！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "世上有这么多宝刀吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_fu_da_jie",
      "text": "馥儿你可退下了！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到这么重。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "宝刀自是不同于一般凡刀。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "站得这么近干吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这把刀虽是毫不起眼，又似有点古朴，但不知如何，我回来后心中不时浮现出它影子，感到它有种说不出的味道来。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "场主真有眼光，不同于一般浅薄之徒。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "谁要你来抬奉我。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我从未见过比这更钝更黯哑无光的刀身，但却有种我也从未之见的高古朴拙的味儿。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "是怎样得来的！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "是阿爷传给爹，爹再传给我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那老头儿对这把刀有甚么话说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "鲁先生说这是二百年前当时天下第一刀法大家'刀霸'凌上人的随身兵器，不知如何会落在家祖手上呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是否真的生了锈，但看来又不是铁锈，而只是刀体本身特有的肉质纹理。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "这是把通灵的宝刀，家祖曾说过有趟遇贼来袭，这把刀竟响个不停来示警哩！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "吹牛皮！你自己听过它叫吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "上次贼来时它刚好休息，所以没有叫。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "耍两招来看看，瞧你有石龙多少成功夫。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你的表情虽似高手，但手法却稀松平庸，唉！枉你们还要付钱学艺。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "请看我这招'繁星点点'！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这样子下去，不用敌人杀你，自己也要累死了哩！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "刀是攻向敌人的，不用力怎成？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你又有甚么拿手本领？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "我比小宁更不行，可以免了吧！",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你好像愈来愈不把我当作场主，不知我说的话就是命令。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不看便不看吧！献丑不如藏拙，乃聪明之举。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "梁治",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "下属有急事上禀场主。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_liang_zhi",
      "text": "大执事请进！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "梁治",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "报告场主，有为数约二千的敌人，出现在牧场西面入口三十里处，该是四大寇的先锋队伍。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_liang_zhi",
      "text": "东面入口外可有动静？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "梁治",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "尚未有报告。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你们可返回宿处，若没有甚么事，就不要四处走动，明白吗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这真令人费解，谁都知飞马牧场比任何坚城更难攻破，为何四大寇竟舍他城攻此呢？定是有阴谋诡计。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "会否只是佯攻此处，目标则是附近的当阳或远安，甚或更远的竟陵呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这更说不通，若我是四大寇的参谋，就会集中全力攻打其中一城，引得牧场劳师远征赴援，再在途中伏击，才是正理。若是兵力分散，来攻牧场的不全军覆没才奇怪。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "鲁妙子发明的理论，最好是用在兵法上，现在我们对四大寇的阴谋，便欠了这'遁去的一'，只要能把这宝贝的一找出来，则敌寇所为便会各安其位。一切变得合情合理！他奶奶的，这宝贝一是甚么家伙呢？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若那个家伙和内奸都是四大寇派来的人，那他们理该在暗中弄鬼，没道理这么明刀明枪来攻的。以牧场的形势而言，里应外合亦起不了甚么作用。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我明白了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "明白了甚么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这定是调虎离山之计，醉翁之意不在酒，而在不再爱我的心上人李秀宁身上。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "说得对，只看李秀宁白天才来，那内奸便向外鬼作报告，外鬼又偷偷离开，便该知与你的梦中情人有关了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "四大寇真是毫不自量，竟敢打秀宁的主意。咦！不对！若开罪李阀对他们有甚么好处呢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "好处可以是多方面的，例如破坏牧场和李阀的关系。又或从李阀的仇人处得到丰厚的报酬和承诺诸如此类。你的脑筋是否因李秀宁而变得迟钝了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "确是有点慌乱，现在该怎办才好？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若我是背后指使四大寇的人，一个活的公主自然比一个香销玉殒的公主更管用。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这背后的主谋会否是李密呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "李密、王世充和薛举都是嫌疑最大的人，可想见四大寇一方面在拖着牧场的主力，另一方面则会派出最强的高手队伍从山区潜入山城，再由内奸接应发动阴谋，我们应否直接和商秀洵说呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "谁知商秀洵会有怎样反应，还是不说为妙，就让我们先查出内奸，到时再对来敌迎头痛击好了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你主内我主外，这该是搏杀四大寇千载一时的良机。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "掉转过来可以吗？就由我负责招呼那四个贼子头。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "主内那个须与李秀宁合作无间，自是非你莫属。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "当你可怜我这失恋的小小子吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你不是想我追求商秀洵吗？今趟说不定就是个机会，异日她知道我出了这么多力，或者感动得委身下嫁哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "还说甚么好兄弟，这么样来陷我于不义。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "仲少能同时在情场战场大展神威，该感激我才是。来吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "到那里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "当然是去见我们的幕后主持人哩！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "下去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若你真想得到'杨公宝库'，必须熟读此书才成。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "text": "先生真知小子的心事。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我死后你才可开盒翻阅，否则若你告诉我看一趟便完全明白，我将会死不瞑目。哈！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "text": "这两盒对我也很有用。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "拿去吧！谁叫我和你们这么有缘哩！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些都是我三十年前制成的小玩意，很多已流落到江湖去，为我赚了无数黄澄澄的金子。现留在箱内的都是我舍不得卖出去的东西。我死后，用得着的你们可拿走，其他就陪我长埋此室吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "只要你们运功扳下铁杆，此室就会在十息之内关闭，再没人可打开来，而且此室会下降十丈，成为我死后的安乐窝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "text": "鲁先生果是名不虚传，只是这种神乎其技的土木机关之学，已足当古往今来此道的第一宗匠了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人生若梦，弹指即过，回首前尘，惟只侮恨交缠，若我有机会从头来过，才没兴趣去碰这些使人沉迷的玩意呢。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那里面有十张精制的面具，可使你们摇身一变成为另一个人，行走江湖时最为方便，且包保没有人能识破，今晚更可派上用场。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论何等精妙的巧器，均只属小道。若倚仗之对修习上乘武道实是有损无益，所以我并不鼓励你们用上它们。这十张面具则是例外。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "text": "先生教训得好，我刚才还生出贪念，想把所有东西都设法运走，现在当然不敢有违先生教诲哩！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 405,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "现在我有些欢喜你了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 409,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "text": "原来先生一直对我没有好感。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 411,
      "line_end": 411
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "也不尽是这样，因我颇精相人之术，见你眉扬眼锐，鼻管气势直贯上庭而尖挺，显是野心既大又不怕铤而走险的人，为善则是万世景仰的英雄，为恶则是不世枭霸，所以总对你有三分戒心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 413,
      "line_end": 415
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "text": "先生既懂相人之道，难道看不出我有颗善良的心吗？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 417,
      "line_end": 419
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这样的肉麻话亏你说得出口来，只从这点就知你好人有限哩！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 421,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这对'飞天神遁'乃我当年倚之逃过祝玉妍追杀的宝贝儿，可以分开使用，能抓穿任何物件，当然要武功高强才可运用自如。尾后的钢环连着长达十丈罕贵的冰蚕蚕丝，凭你们的真气，可使钢爪灵活如人手，蚕丝则可长可短，但我今天没有甚么精神详说，你们自己研究好了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "书可以留下，你们各选一个面具后，便可带同天遁神抓去趁热闹，记得回来向我详述克敌制胜的过程。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 435
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知是李阀鸿运当头，还是四大寇倒足霉头，竟惹上你这两个家伙。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 106,
      "line_start": 437,
      "line_end": 439
    }
  ],
